 Anyway, so I was the youth pastor for a little while,

18
00:00:35,920 --> 00:00:40,000
 and youth work is a great way to get to know

19
00:00:40,000 --> 00:00:41,520
 how to do ministry.

20
00:00:41,520 --> 00:00:44,520
 And one of the things I got to do was to take youth groups

21
00:00:44,520 --> 00:00:45,920
 on mission trips.

22
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:48,560
 And so this was about 17 years ago.

23
00:00:48,560 --> 00:00:51,660
 I was just a kid back then, so I was like a big kid

24
00:00:51,660 --> 00:00:54,560
 taking some little kids to a foreign country,

25
00:00:54,560 --> 00:00:56,200
 a place I didn't know the language,

26
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:58,560
 I didn't know the people, to serve a group.

27
00:00:58,560 --> 00:01:00,840
 I didn't even really know who I was connecting with.

28
