 This is when I discovered that Hainanese chicken rice

35
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:19,520
 is not really from Hainan Island, okay?

36
00:01:19,520 --> 00:01:20,920
 Amongst many other things.

37
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:22,560
 So we were looking for a place to have dinner.

38
00:01:22,560 --> 00:01:25,520
 I was walking around with me and a bunch of about 12

39
