 other kids, teenagers, preteens, and so we found this place.

40
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:33,600
 It was a cheap hot pot place, so I thought, perfect.

41
00:01:33,600 --> 00:01:37,600
 Hong Kong kids, cheap hot pot, perfect place for dinner.

42
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,800
 And so we decided to have dinner there.

43
00:01:39,800 --> 00:01:41,440
 And when we walked in, we discovered, actually,

44
