00:20:47,600 --> 00:20:49,940
 He makes promises that he cannot keep.

508
00:20:49,940 --> 00:20:53,480
 It's almost like a pathetic and hopeless pleading.

509
00:20:53,480 --> 00:20:55,960
 But remember, right, there is no way,

510
00:20:55,960 --> 00:20:58,260
 this man knows there's no way he can pay back

